&lt;li&gt;Interface with NRTL / external agencies for certification, specifying and performing testing, defining which standards are appropriate, and clarifying intent of standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with customers to validate Fulfil equipment meets their internal safety requirements and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help develop functional safety architectures for new automation systems and design upgrades to existing systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review plans and specifications for new machinery and equipment to ensure they meet safety requirements and are designed for operator safety&lt;/li&gt;
