&lt;li&gt;Identify and correct potential hazards by inspecting facilities, machinery, and safety equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in safety system implementation at new sites and performance of on-site equipment safety testing and validation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with operations to write safety manuals for Fulfil equipment that will be provided to customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
